Opinion 'I'LL NEVER LET THIS ONE GO' Britain’s youngest mum who gave birth at 12 after being raped by her brother reveals she is pregnant by fiance 
Tressa Middleton first fell pregnant aged 11 after she was raped by her brother and the child was adopted aged two By FELIX ALLEN
